name: PsyopCoin
description: The PSYOP token ($PSYOP) drives a decentralized initiative to expose systemic flaws in modern society and financial systems. Its purpose is to empower a global community for collective research and transparent information dissemination. Utility includes incentivizing contributions and providing access to analytical tools for critical analysis. Built on blockchain, it fosters verifiable information sharing for greater transparency and accountability, aiming to cultivate a more critically aware populace.
